1. Free refers to no per transaction fees for receipt of ACH Bank Transfer payment. Subscription to QuickBooks Online and/or optional monthly Payments plan may be required. QuickBooks Payments account subject to eligibility criteria, credit and application approval.
Getting Paid 2X faster based on U.S. QuickBooks Online invoices using invoice tracking & payments features from Oct 2014 – April 2015
