*Includes magnetic swipe and EMV inserted “dip” transactions.
QuickBooks Payments account subject to eligibility criteria, credit and application approval. See Important Info, Pricing, Acceptable Use Policy and Merchant Agreement. Terms, conditions, prices, payment, features and services are subject to change.
 
Mobile payments requires download and use of the QuickBooks Online mobile app or the GoPayment mobile app; click here to view GoPayment compatible devices. Mobile card reader is a standalone device, available at no additional cost to new Intuit QuickBooks Payments customers.

2. #1 online professional tax software” statement is based on Intuit internal data of the number of paid users of Intuit Tax Online for Tax Year 2014 compared to publicly available statements from competitors for the same time period.


 
 
























